                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18110109-35-defend417 t18110109-35-punish211"></join>
               Transported for Seven Years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>GREEN, <rs id="t18110109-35-verdict212" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18110109-35-verdict212" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
               NOT GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex jury, before Mr. justice Le Blanc.</p>
